prepare.qsub
Prepares the input files needed for machine learning data generation.

find_crack_tip.qsub
Runs find_crack_tip.m for the crack-tip detection stage. 

ref_find_crack_tip.m
MATLAB code used for crack-tip detection. This script extracts localized domains around the propagating crack front to construct the ML dataset.

predict.qsub
Runs predict.py for ML prediction tasks.

predict.py
Python script for the trained Transformer model predicts crack propagation in localized sub-domains.

combine_predict.qsub
Runs combine_predict.m to combine predicted crack-path segments back into the global domain, reconstructing the full trajectory.

ref_combine_predict.m
MATLAB code that combines predicted crack-path segments back into the global domain.

file.txt
Contains the time-step count information.
